  "original_title": "\u0b9f\u0bc6\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b92\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b95\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ministry of Health has declared today as Dengue Eradication Day",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Today (25) has been declared as Dengue Eradication Special Day. The Ministry of Health has informed that the spread of dengue fever is increasing across the country.",
        "Director General of Health Services Dr. Asela Gunawardena commented on this,",
        "He mentioned that more than 43,000 people have been affected by dengue fever so far this year.",
        "The Ministry of Health has mentioned that the breeding grounds of the virus have been found in government and private institutions, schools, premises where construction works are taking place, factories and public places.",
        "Meanwhile, the Ministry of Health has requested the public to be vigilant regarding the symptoms of the disease due to the spread of Dengue Corona and Influenza.",
        "Dr. Sudath Samaraweera, director of the National Dengue Eradication Unit, urged to seek medical attention immediately if fever persists for more than 24 hours."
      ],
